text: Sunkist Growers, Incorporated is an American citrus growers' non-stock membership cooperative. It is headquartered in Valencia, California. It is the largest fresh produce shipper in the United States, the most diversified citrus processing and marketing operation in the world, and one of California's largest landowners. It was founded in 1893. Category:American food companies Category:1893 establishments in the United States
